Simplify code relating to get_info
Let get_info accept a FrameInfo so there's no need to check for frames vs FrameInfo
Leave the type checking for frames/tracebacks/FrameInfo to get_info
Reduce the calls and indirection to get_info so it's easier to navigate the code and see where get_info is called
